settings.description: The sewers have been filled with water, possibly too much to handle for Mario.
The destroyed constructions were destroyed by the boss bass before the level,enjoy.

I'm sure every level set needs an underwater stage! And where there is water, there is bound to be a frog somewhere in it!
Difficulty: 4/5
Suppose it's time for an old washed up mario flash level maker to step foot into a new light... with a new honestly great level making program as well! hopefully this level's fun too!
My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.
